Package covidSimulation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Agent
    Super-class of all agents.
    ContextCreator
    Implementation of the ContextBuidler interface : builds a Context by adding projections, agents and so forth.
    DeceasedAgent
    This class represents the "deceased" agents.
    DynamicAgentStyle
    Class used to display the agents dynamically.
    InfectedAgent
    Abstract class that represents all infected agents.
    InfectedWithoutSymptomsAgent
    This class represents agents who have been infected but that have no symptoms.
    InfectedWithSymptomsAgent
    This class represents agents who have been infected but and have symptoms.
    RecoveredAgent
    A person who has recovered can not anymore be infected because she has developped antibodies against Covid.
    SusceptibleAgent
    This type of agent has never been infected by the Covid.
